hadiths[119]{hadithnumber,text}:
3736,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko waleemey ki dawat di jaey to chahiye ke wo us mein hazir ho.''"
3737,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani zikr kya aur mazeed kaha : ''agar roza na rakha ho to khaney mein shareek ho jaey aur agar rozey se ho to (sahibe-tuaam (khana) ke liye) dua karey.''
3738,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumhen tumhara bhai dawat dey to qubul kerni chahiye, shaadi (ka waleema) ho ya uski manind (jaisi) koi aur.''"
3739,"Ibne Musaffa ne kaha hamein baqiya ne bayan kiya, usney kaha : hamen Zubaidi ne Naafe se Ayub ki sanad ke sath usi ke ham-maani riwayat kiya."
3740,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey dawat di gaee ho usey chahiye ke qubul kar ley, phir agar chahey to khana kha ley aur agar chahey to na khaye.''"
3741,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey dawat di gaee aur usney usey qubul na kiya to usney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki, aur jo shakhs bin bulaey kisi dawat mein ja pahuncha, to wo un mein chor bin kar dakhil hua aur lutera bin kar nikla. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : (raawi) Aban bin Tariq Majhool hai."
3742,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke sab se bura waleema wo hai jis mein maldaron aur ameeron ko bulaya jaey aur miskinon aur faqiron ko chhod diya jaey aur jo dawat mein nahin aaya usney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki.
3743,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein Ummul-momenin Hazrat Zenab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke nikah ka zikr aa gaya to unhoney kaha : maine nahin dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni kisi biwi ke waleeme mein is qadr ehtimam kiya ho jitna unke mauqe par waleeme mein kiya tha. aapney eik bakri se waleema kiya.
3744,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ummul-momenin Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ke nikah mein sattu aur khajoor se waleema kiya tha.
3745,"Abdullah bin Usman ne qabeela saqeeb ke eik kaaney aadmi se riwayat ki, usey Maroof kaha jata tha, yani uski madah (tareef) ki jati thi. agar uska naam Zuhair bin Usman nahin to mujhey maloom nahin ke uska kya naam tha? usney riwayat kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beshak waleema pehley din haq (lazim) hai, doosrey din neki hai aur teesrey din shohra aur dikhlaao hai. Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne eik aadmi se naqal kiya ke Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) ko pehley din dawat di gaee to qubul ki, doosrey din bulaya gaya to qubul kiya, teesrey din bulaya gaya to qubul na kiya aur kaha : ye log shohra aur dikhlaao chahtey hain."
3746,Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab se ye qissa bayan kiya. kaha ke teesrey din bulaya gaya to dawat qubul na ki aur pegham laney waley ko kankar dey maara.
3747,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Madina tashrif laye to aapney eik oont ya gaey zibeh ki thi.
3748,"Hazrat Abu-Shuraih ka'bi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ka Allah aur aakhirat ke din par emaan hai usey chahiye ke apney mehman ki izzat karey, khoob khidmat aur madaaraat eik din raat hai, mehmani teen din hoti hai, uskey baad sadqa hai. mehman ke liye halal nahin ke apney mezban ke paas deraa dal ley ke uskey liye mashaqqat aur bojh bin jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ba-sand Haris bin Miskeen , Ash'hab se marwi (bayan) hai ke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman : ( جائزته يوم وليلة (ka mafhoom puchha gaya , to unhoney kaha ke eik din raat uski khoob izzat afzaai karey, usey tohfa dey aur uska khoob khayal karey aur teen din tak mehmani hai."
3749,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mezbani teen din hai jo uskey alawa ho, wo sadqa hai.''"
3750,"Hazrat Abu-Kareema (Miqdam bin Maadikarib) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik raat ki ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi) her musalman par haq lazim (wajib) hai. jo shakhs kisi ke sehan mein utrey to ziyaafat us par qarz hai, mehman chahey to wasul kar ley aur agar chahey to chhod dey.''"
3751,"Hazrat Miqdam (bin Maadikarib) Abu-Kareema (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi qaum ka mehman ho phir wo ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi) se mehroom rahey to uski nusrat karna her musalman par wajib hai yahan tak ke wo un se apni eik raat ki ziyaafat hasil kar ley. uski kheti se aur maal se .''"
3752,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke ham ne arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap hamein rawana farmatey hain, ham kisi qaum ke yahan padaaw kartey hain aur wo hamari mehmani nahin kartey to aap ki kya raey hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein farmaya : ''agar tum kisi qaum ke yahan padaaw karo to agar wo tumharey liye us chiz ka kahen jo mehman ke layaq hai to usey qubul kar lo, agar wo aisa na keren to un se apna haq ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi ka haq) wasul karo jo layaq aur munasib ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is mein daleel hai ke insan apna haq wasul kar sakta hai."
3753,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney Sura Nisaa ki aayat (29) ki tafseer mein farmaya (لَا تَأْكُلُوا أَمْوَالَكُمْ بَيْنَكُمْ . . ۔) ''tum aapas main eik doosrey ka maal batil tareeqey se mat khao , siwaye iskey ke aapas ki razamandi se tijarat ho.'' is aayat ke utarney par log eik doosrey ke yahan khana khaney mein harj samajhtey they. phir sura Noor ki aayat (61) ne usko mansookh kar diya. farmaya : (لَيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ جُنَاحٌ أَنْ تَأْكُلُوا مِنْ بُيُوتِكُمْ . . . أَشْتَاتًا) ''tum par koi harj nahin ke apney gharon se khao ya apney baap dada ke gharon se ya apni maaon ke gharon se ya apney bhaiyon ke gharon se ya apni behnon ke gharon se ya apney chachaon ke gharon se ya apni phuphiyon ke gharon se ya apney mamuon ke gharon se ya apni khalaon ke gharon se ya un gharon se jin ki kunjiyon ke tum Malik ho ya apney doston ke gharon sey, us mein bhi koi harj nahin ke tum sab sath mil kar khao ya alag alag.'' (isi tarah) koi ghani apney ehle ke kisi fard ko khaney ki dawat deta to wo kehta ke main uskey khaney mein harj samajhta hun, koi aur miskeen iska mujh se ziyada haq daar hai. chunanche is aayat ke zariey se halal thehraya gaya hai ke jis par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho wo kha liya keren aur (aisey hi) ehle-kitab ka khana bhi halal kar diya gaya."
3754,Ikrima (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kaha kartey they : bila-shuba Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne muqable bazi mein aa kar khilaney walon ka khana khaney se mana farmaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Jarir ke aksar shagrid is riwayat mein ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka naam zikr nahin kartey. albatta Harun Nahwi ne unka naam liya hai. Hammad bin Zaid ne bhi ibne-Abbas ka zikr nahin kiya. (yani unki riwayat mursal hui .)
3755,"Hazrat Safina Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik aadmi ne Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ki dawat ki aur unke liye khana tayyar kiya (aur unke ghar bhej diya) Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : agar ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bula len aur wo bhi hamarey sath tanaawul farma (kha) len (to bahut khoob ho) chunanche unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dawat di aur aap tashrif ley aaye. aapney apna haath darwazey ki chaukhat par rakha aur eik munaqqash parda dekha jo ghar ki eik janib mein lagaya gaya tha, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis ho liye . Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kiya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se milen aur maloom keren ke kis chiz ne aap ko wapis lotaya hai. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey gaya aur arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap kis wajeh se wapis aagey hain? aapney farmaya : ''mujhey layaq nahin ya kaha ke Nabi ko layaq nahin ke naqsh aur nigaar waley ghar mein dakhil ho.''"
3756,"Eik sahabi se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab do shakhs dawat deney waley ikhattey ho jaeyn to uski dawat qubul kar jis ka darwaza un mein se ziyada qarib ho kyonkey jis ka darwaza ziyada qarib ho usi-ki ham-saayegi ziyada qarib hoti hai. aur agar un mein se eik pehley aaya hai to pehley aaney waley ki qubul kar.''"
3757,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ka raat ka khana rakh diya gaya ho aur Namaz ki iqaamat bhi ho gaee ho to (Namaz ke liye) na uthey yahan tak ke khaney se farigh ho jaey.'' Musaddad ne mazeed kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah (bin Umar) (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke liye raat ka khana rakh diya jata . . . ya shaam ka khana tayyar ho jata . . . to wo khaney se farigh ho janey tak na uthtey chahey (chahe) iqaamat sun letey ya Imam ki qirat sun rahey hotey."
3758,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khaney ya kisi aur wajeh se Namaz ko muakhkhar (der) na kiya jaey.''"
3759,Janab Abdullah bin Ubaid bin Umair ne kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke daur ki baat hai ke main apney walid (Ubaid bin Umair) ke sath Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath baitha hua tha ke Ibad bin Abdullah bin Zuber ne kaha : ham ne suna hai ke) Namaz se pehley ( ishaaiye (raat ke khaney) se ibtida ki jaey. to Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : afsos tum par ! bhala unka ishaaiya kya hota tha? kya tum samajhtey ho ke tumharey baap ke ishaaiye ki tarah hota tha? (yani kya tarah-tarah ke khaney hotey they?)
3760,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) se nikley to aap ko khana pesh kiya gaya. Sahaba ne kaha : kya aap ke liye wuzu ka pani na ley ayen? aapney farmaya : ''mujhey wuzu ka hukm usi waqt hai jab main Namaz ke liye khada hun.''
3761,Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Taurat mein padha ke khaney se pehley wuzu kar lena baaise-barkat hota hai. maine ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr ki to aapney farmaya : ''khaney ki barkat wuzu mein hai ke khaney se pehley kiya jaey aur baad mein bhi. aur Janab Sufiyan khaney se pehley wuzu karna makruh samajhtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ye riwayat zaeef hai.
3762,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik pahadi ki ghaati ki taraf se tashrif laye . aap qazaey-hajat se (pakhana-peshab karke) aaye they aur hamarey samney dhaal par khajuren rakhi thin. ham ne aap ko dawat di to aapney hamarey sath mil kar tanaawul farmaeen (khaeen) aur pani ko haath bhi nahin lagaya.
3763,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kabhi kisi khaney mein aeb nahin nikala . aap ki tabiat chahti to tanaawul farma (kha) letey agar napasand kartey to chhod detey."
3764,"Wahshi bin Harab apney walid se aur wo (Wahshi ke) dada sahabi ( Wahshi bin Harab) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke as-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham khatey hain magar sair nahin hotey . aapney farmaya : ''shayad tum log alehda alehda ho kar khatey ho?'' unhoney kaha : haan . aapney farmaya : ''ikhattey ho kar khaya karo aur us par Allah ka naam liya karo, us mein tumharey liye barkat paida kar di jaeygi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : jab tum kisi dawat mein shareek ho aur ishaaiya (khana) samney rakh diya jaey to jab tak ghar wala ijazat na dey mat khao."
3765,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''insan jab apney ghar mein dakhil hotey huey Allah ka naam leta hai aur phir apney khaney par bhi Allah ka zikr karta hai to shaitan kehta hai : tumharey liye yahan na raat ka koi thikana hai aur na raat ka khana. aur jab insan dakhil hotey waqt Allah ka zikr na karey to shaitan kehta hai : tumhen raat ka thikana mil gaya aur jab khaney par bhi Allah ka naam na ley tu kehta hai : tumhen raat ke thikaney ke sath-sath khana bhi mil gaya.''
3766,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham log jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khaney mein shareek hotey to ham mein se koi khaney mein haath na daalta jab tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shuru na kar letey. chunanche eik martaba ham aap ke sath khaney mein shareek they ke eik badwi aaya goya usey dhakela ja raha tha, isliye wo aagey badha ke khaney mein apna haath daley to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska haath pakad liya. phir eik chhoti bachchi aai goya usey (bhi) dhakela ja raha tha, usney bhi aagey badh kar apna haath khaney mein dalna chaha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska haath bhi pakad liya aur farmaya : ''jis khaney par Allah ka naam na liya gaya ho shaitan usey apney liye halal samajh leta hai. wo us badwi ko laya taake uskey zariey se khana hasil kar sakey , magar maine uska haath pakad liya aur us bachchi ko laya taake uskey zariey se khana ley sakey , to maine uska haath bhi pakad liya . qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! bila-shuba uska haath , un (dono) ke haathon ke sath merey haath mein hai.''"
3767,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jab koi khana khaney lagey to chahiye ke Allah taala ka naam zikr karey, agar shuru mein bhool jaey to chahiye ke yun kahiye (بسم الله أوله وآخره ) ''Allah ke naam se is (khaney) ke shuru mein aur aakhir mein bhi.''"
3768,"Hazrat Umayya bin Makhshi (Raziallahu anhu) eik sahabi they unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they jabkey eik aadmi khana kha raha tha usney بسم اللہ nahin padhi thi. yahan tak ke jab uskey khaney se eik luqma baqi reh gaya to usney usey apney munh ki taraf uthatey huey kaha : (بسم الله أوله وآخره) ''Allah ke naam se is (khaney) ke shuru mein aur aakhir mein bhi .''to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hansney lagey aur farmaya : ''shaitan uskey sath khaye ja raha tha jab usney Allah ka naam liya to jo kuchh uskey pet mein tha usney wo sab qai karkey nikal diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Jabir bin Subh , Sulaiman bin Harab ke naana hain."
3769,Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa (Wahab bin Abdullah) (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main sahara lekar (tek laga kar) nahin khata.''
3770,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey (kisi kaam sey) bheja. phir main aap ke paas wapis hazir hua to maine dekha ke aap khajuren kha rahey they aur iq-aa ki haalat mein (peeth key bal) baithey huey they.
3771,Janab Shuaib bin Abdullah bin Amr apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi nahin dekha gaya ke aapney takiya laga kar khana khaya ho ya do aadmiyon ne bhi aap ki eidiyaan rondi hon (aisey nahin hua ke aap takabburaana andaz se aagey aagey chalen aur log aap ke peechchey hon.)
3772,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jab koi khana khaney lagey to piyaley ke ooper (darmiyan) se na khaye balke nichey (eik janib) se khaye. bila-shuba barkat uskey ooper ki taraf se utarti hai.''"
3773,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik bahut bada thaal tha, jisey (غراء) kaha jata tha, usey chaar aadmi uthatey they. jab chaasht ka waqt hua aur unhoney zuhaa ki Namaz padh li to us thaal ko laya gaya jabkey us mein sareed banaya gaya tha (yani shorbey mein roti bhigoi gaee thi). sab log uskey gird jama ho gaey. jab logon ki kasrat ho gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghutney tek liye . eik badwi ne kaha : baithney ka ye kaisa andaz hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne mujhey nek khoo banda banaya hai, na ke mutakabbir sarkash.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''iske aas-paas se khao aur choti ko chhod do, is mein barkat hogi.''"
3774,"Janab Salim apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaney ke mutalliq do baaton se mana farmaya hai. eik aisey dasterkhaan par baithna jis par sharab pi jaey, doosrey pet ke bal ondhey let kar khana. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye hadees Jaafar ne Zohri se nahin suni ye riwayat munkir hai."
3775,Harun bin Zaid bin Abi Zarqa ne kaha hamein merey walid ne bayan kiya unhoney kaha hamein Jaafar ne bayan kiya ke usey Zohri se ye hadees pahunchi.
3776,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khaye to apney daain haath se khaye aur jab piye to apney daain haath se piye , bila-shuba shaitan apney baeyn haath se khata aur apney baeyn se peeta hai.''"
3777,"Hazrat umr bin Abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey qarib ho jao, Allah ka naam lo , ( بسم الله ( padho) daain haath se khao aur apney samney se khao.''"
3778,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gosht chhuri se kaat kar mat khao, kyonkey ye ajmiyon ka tariqa hai, balke daanton se kaat kar aur noch kar khao, is tarah ye ziyada lazzat deta hai aur khoob hazam hota hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye riwayat qawi nahin hai."
3779,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khana kha raha tha aur apney haath se haddi par se gosht juda kar raha tha. isliye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haddi utha kar apney munh se lagao (yani noch kar khao) beshak is tarah ye ziyada lazeez lagta hai aur hazam khoob hota hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Usman ne Safwan se nahin suna aur ye riwayat mursal hai.
3780,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bakri ki aisi haddi bahut pasand thi jis par se gosht utaar liya gaya ho aur thoda baqi ho.''
3781,Janab Abu-Dawud (Tiyalisi) (Rahimahullah) ne isi sanad se riwayat kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dasti ka gosht bahut pasand tha. bayan kiya ke aap ko dasti ke gosht hi mein zahar deney ki koshish ki gaee thi aur ye kaaristaani yahudiyon ne ki thi.
3782,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke eik darzi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khaney par bulaya jo usney tayyar kiya tha. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath us khaney mein gaya tha. isliye usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jau ki roti aur shorbaa pesh kiya jis mein kaddu aur khushk gosht tha. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) piyaley ke atraaf se kaddu ke tukdey talash kar rahey they, chunanche us din ke baad mein kaddu ko bahut pasand kerney laga hun."
3783,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke roti ka sareed aur hees ka sareed Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sab khaanon se ziyada pasand tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke ye zaeef hai.
3784,"Janab Qabisa bin Halab Tilaai apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna jabkey eik aadmi ne aap se sawal kiya tha ke kuchh khaney aisey hain jinkey khaney mein, main harj samajhta hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi (halal) chiz terey seeney mein shak aur shubha na daley, is se to nasraniyon (rahibon) ke mushabeh ho jaeyga.''"
3785,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne gandagi khor janwar khaney aur uska doodh peeney se mana farmaya hai.
3786,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne gandagi khor janwar ke doodh se mana farmaya hai.
3787,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne gandagi khor oont par sawari karney aur uska doodh peeney se mana farmaya hai.
3788,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khaibar waley din gadhon ke gosht se mana farmaya aur ghodon ke gosht ki ijazat di thi.
3789,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke ham ne khaibar ke roz ghodey , khachchar aur gadhey zibeh kiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khachcharon aur gadhon se mana farma diya lekin ghodon se mana nahin farmaya."
3790,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghodey , khachchar aur gadhey ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya hai. Hewa bin Shuraih ne mazeed kaha : darindon mein se har naab-daar (kachli waley) janwer se bhi mana farmaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Imam Malik ka bhi yehi qol hai (yani ghoda makruh hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke . . . ghodey ke gosht mein koi harj nahin magar us par amal nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : aur ye (riwayat jis mein ghodey ke gosht khaney ki mumaaniat hai) mansookh hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ki eik jamaat ne ghodey ka gosht khaya hai. un mein Hazrat ibne-Zubair , Fazaala bin Ubaid , Anas bin Malik , Asma binte-Abi Bakr , Suwaid bin Ghafala aur Alqama (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ka naam aata hai. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Quraishi log ghoda zibeh kiya kartey they."
3791,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main eik nau-nawela mazboot ladka tha. maine eik khargosh shikar kiya, phir maine usey bhoon liya . to Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey uska pichhlaa dhad de-kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja. main usey aap ke paas ley aaya to aapney usey qubul farma liya."
3792,Abu-Khalid bin Huweris ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) maqame-saffaah mein they. Muhammad (bin Khalid) ne wazahat ki ke ye jagah Makka mein hai. isliye eik aadmi khargosh lekar aaya jo usney shikar kiya tha. usney kaha : aey Abdullah bin Amr ! aap kiya kehtey hain? unhoney kaha : ye janwar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya gaya tha jabkey main (aap ke paas) baitha hua tha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne na usey khaya aur na khaney se mana farmaya aur kaha ke isey haiz aata hai.
3793,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke unki khaala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ghi , saandey aur paneer ka hadiya bheja . aapney ghi aur paneer kha liya magar saandey ko tabiyat ke na chahney par chhod diya. taaham (fir-bhi) usey aap ke dasterkhaan par khaya gaya , agar haram hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke dasterkhaan par hergiz na khaya jata."
3794,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) , Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo (Khalid (Raziallahu anhu)) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar gaey unhon-ne bhoona hua saandaa pesh kiya gaya. aapney apna haath badhaya to baaz khawatin ne jo Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein thin kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jo khaney lagey hain unhen uskey mutalliq bata do. isliye Sahaba ne kaha : ye saandaa hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna haath utha liya. Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kiya ye haram hai? aapney farmaya : ''nahin, lekin ye merey watan mein nahin paey jatey isliye main tabaee karaahat ki bina par is se bachta hun.'' Khalid ne kaha : phir maine usey apni taraf khinch liya aur kha liya jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dekh rahey they."
3795,"Hazrat Sabit bin Wadeeaa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham eik lashkar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, hamein saandey miley . main un mein se eik bhoon kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaya aur aap ke samney rakha. aapney eik tinkaa liya aur is se uski ungliyan shumar kin. phir farmaya : ''bani-Israel ki eik qaum ko zameen ke janwaron ki shakal mein maskh kar diya gaya tha, mujhey nahin maloom wo kaun se janwar they.'' kaha ke phir aapney na usey khaya aur na mana kiya."
3796,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Shibl (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saandey ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya hai.
3797,"Buraih bin umr bin Safina apney walid se wo (unke baap umr bin Safeena) unke dada se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath surkhab ''paani ki eik chidiya'' ka gosht khaya tha."
3798,Janab Milqaam bin Talab apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke unhoney kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat mein raha hun magar maine aap se hashraat (zameen ke andar rehney waley janwaron) ki hurmat ke baarey mein kuchh nahin suna.
3799,"Esa bin Numaila apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas tha ke un se kaantedar janglee choohen (saih) ke mutalliq sawal kiya gaya to unhoney Sura Anaam ki ye aayat tilawat farmaai (قُلْ لَا أَجِدُ فِيمَا أُوحِيَ إِلَيَّ مُحَرَّمًا . . . الخ) ''keh dijiye ke bazariey wahi jo ehkam merey paas aaye hain un mein se main kisi khaney waley ke liye koi chiz jisey wo khana chahey haram nahin paata siwaye uskey ke wo murdar ho ya behta hua khoon ho ya khinzir ka gosht , beshak wo napak hai ya wo fisq hai ke (zibeh kartey waqt) us par Allah ke siwa kisi aur ka naam pukara gaya ho, phir jo shakhs majboor ho jaey, (ba-sharte-ke) wo sarkashi karney wala aur had se guzarney wala na ho, to beshak aap ka Rab bada bakhshney wala, nihayat rehem kerney wala hai.'' majlis mein se badi umr ke eik aadmi ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas uska zikr hua tha to aapney farmaya: ''khabees (gandey) janwaron mein se eik khabees (gandaa) janwer hai.'' Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye farmaya hai to phir baat wohi (sahih) hai jo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaai hai jis ka hamein ilm nahin."
3800,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Islam se pehley log kaee chizon ko khatey aur kaee ko napasand kartey huey chhod detey they. tu Allah taala ne apna Nabi, Nabi banakar bheja , apni kitab nazil ki, halal ko halal aur haram ko haram thehraya . to jis ko usney halal kiya wo halal hai aur jis ko usney haram kiya wo haram hai aur jiskey baarey mein khamoshi ikhtiyar ki wo maaf hai aur sura inaam ki aayat tilawat farmaai (قُلْ لَا أَجِدُ فِيمَا أُوحِيَ إِلَيَّ مُحَرَّمًا . . . الخ) ''keh dijiye ke bazariey wahi jo ehkam merey paas aaye hain un mein main kisi khaney waley ke liye koi chiz jisey wo khana chahey haram nahin paata siwaey iske ke wo murdar ho ya behta hua khoon ho ya khinzir ka gosht, beshak wo napak hai ya wo fisq hai ke (zibeh kartey waqt) us par Allah ke siwa kisi aur ka naam pukara gaya ho, phir jo shakhs majboor ho jaey, (b-sharte-ke) wo sarkashi kerney wala aur had se guzarney wala na ho, to beshak aap ka Rab bada bakhshney wala, nihayat rehem kerney wala hai.''"
3801,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se lagad-bagad ke mutalliq puchha to aapney farmaya : ''wo shikar hai agar usey mohrim shikar karey to usko eik mendhaa fidya dena hoga.''
3802,"Hazrat Abu Sa'alba khushni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne har kachliyon wala darinda khaney se mana farmaya hai."
3803,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne her kachli waley darindey aur her panjey-daar perindey ke khaney se mana farmaya hai."
3804,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabrdar ! kachliyon wala darinda , paaltu gadha aur kisi zimmi ( kafir (ka gira pada maal halal nahin hain siwaye uskey ke uska Malik us maal se be parwa ho, aur jo koi kisi qom ke paas jaey aur wo uski mehmani na keren to uskey liye jayez hai ke un se apni mehmani ke barabar kuch le-ley .''"
3805,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke roz her kachli wala darinda aur panjey-daar perinda khana mana farmaya."
3806,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwa khaibar mein shareek tha. chunanche yahudi ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ( aaye aur shikayat ki ke log ( musalman ( unke baadon par chadh dodey hain (yani maal maweshi loot liye hain. ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabrdar ! muaahid ( zimmi) logon ka maal halal nahin siwaye iskey ke sharae aur usooli haq ho, tum par paaltu gadhey , ghodey , khachar , kachliyon waley darindey aur panje-daar perindey haram hain.''"
3807,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne billi ki qeemat se mana farmaya hai. ibn Abdul-Malik ki riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne billi ke khaney aur uski qeemat ke khaney se mana farmaya hai.
3808,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke roz hamen gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya aur hukm diya ke ham ghodon ka gosht khaeyn. Amr ne kaha : maine ye riwayat Abul-Shaa-Saa ko batai to unhoney kaha ke Hakam (bin Amr ( Ghifari ( Basra mein) hamarey paas they wo bhi yehi kehtey they. magar is '' bahar '' ne uska inkar kya hai. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) murad hain.
3809,"Hazrat Ghalib bin Abjar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham qehat se dochaar ho gaey . merey paas koi aisi chiz na thi jo main apney ghar walon ko khila sakta. sirf chand gadhey hi they jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne paaltu gadhon ka gosht haram farma diya tha. chunanche main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham qehat mein mubtala hain aur merey paas koi maal nahin jo main apney ghar walon ko khila sakun siwaye motey motey gadhon ke aur aapney paaltu gadhon ka gosht haram qarar diya hai? aapney farmaya : '' apney ghar walon ko apney motey gadhon mein se khila do , maine unhen isliye haram kya hai ke ye basti ki gandagi khatey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke sanad mein mazkur Abdur-Rehman ye ibn Maaqil hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko Shoba ne Ubaid abul-Hasan se riwayat kya hai, unhoney Abdur-Rehman bin Maaqil sey, unhoney Abdur-Rehman bin Bishr se unhoney Muzena ke kuch logon sey, (unhoney bayan kya) ke qabeela muzena ke sardar Abjar ya ibne-Abjar ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya tha."
3810,"ibne-Maaqil qabeela muzena ke do aadmiyon se riwayat kartey hain, un mein se eik doosrey se riwayat karta hai. eik Abdullah bin Amr bin Uwem hai aur doosra ghalib bin Abjar. Musaair ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke ye ghalib hi tha jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya tha. aur ye riwayat bayan ki ."
3811,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke roz paaltu gadhon ke gosht , gandagi ( gandagi ( khaney waley janweron ki sawari aur unka gosht khaney se mana farmaya tha."
3812,Abu Yaafoor kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) se suna jabke maine un se tiddi ke mutalliq sawal kya to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath chhe ya saat ghazawat mein shirkat ki hai. ham usey khaya kartey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey sath hotey they.
3813,"Janab Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se tiddi ke mutalliq sawal kya gaya to aapney farmaya : '' ( ye ( Allah ke bahut badey lashkaron mein se hai, na main usey khaata hun aur na haram thehrata hun. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : us riwayat ko Motamir ne apney walid sey, usney abu-Usman se aur usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya. is sanad mein Salman ka zikr nahin."
3814,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya gaya. aapney mazkura hadees ki manind farmaya. . . aapney farmaya : ''ye Allah ka bahut bada lashkar hai. Ali (bin Abdullah ( ne kaha hai ke ابوالعوام ( الجزار (ka naam '' فائد '' hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko Hammad bin Salma ne Abul-Awam sey, usney abu-Usman sey, usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya hai aur Salman ka zikr nahin kya."
3815,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' samandar jo bahir phenk dey ya pani peechey hat janey ki soorat mein jo zameen par reh jaey usey kha lo aur jo us mein mar gaee ho aur ooper teer aaye to usey mat khao . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees ko Sufiyan Sauri , Ayub aur Hammad ne abu-Zubair se riwayat kya hai aur unhoney usey Hazrat Jabir par moquf kya hai. aur dusri sanad se ye riwayat musnad marfoo bayan ki gaee hai jo zaeef hai. yani ibne-abi Zi'ib ne bayan kya abu-Zubair sey, unhoney Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se."
3816,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne ( Madina ke qarib) Harra maqam par padaaw kya. uskey sath uskey biwi bachey bhi they. (wahan ke) eik aadmi ne us se kaha ke meri oontni gum ho gaee hai agar tumhen miley to usey pakad lena . chunanche wo usey mil gaee magar uska Malik na mila . phir wo oontni bimar ho gaee . to us shakhs ki biwi ne kaha ke usko nahar ( zibeh ( kar lo . magar wo na maana aur bil-aakhir wo mar gaee . to aurat ne kaha ke uska chamda utaar lo ke ham uski charbi aur gosht khushk kar lein aur khaeyn . to aadmi ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochh lun . chunanche wo aap ki khidmat mein aaya aur aap se puchha to aapney farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas kuch hai jo tumhen us se be parwa kar dey ?'' usney kaha : nahin, aapney farmaya : '' tab tum usey kha saktey ho.'' phir us oontni ka Malik aa gaya to usney usey sari tafsil batai to usney kaha : tum ne usey nahar ( zibeh ( kyon na kar liya? usney jawab diya mujhey tum se haya aai .) ke kahin tum ye na samjho ke usney heeley bahaney se oontni kaat khai hai. ("
3817,Hazrat Fajee Aamiri (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur puchha : kya hamarey liye murdar halal nahin hai? aapney farmaya : '' tumhara tuaam kya hai? '' ham ne kaha : ghabuq aur sabooh. Abu Nuem kehtey hain ke Aqba (bin Wahab) ne mujhey uski wazahat ki ke eik piyala doodh subh aur eik piyala doodh raat ko. kaha : merey baap ki qasam! ye to badi sakht bhook hai. chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke liye us haalat mein murdar ko halal qarar diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke din ke aakhir mein pi janey wali chiz ko ghabuq aur din ke shuru mein pi janey wali ko sabooh kehtey hain.
3818,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mera ji chah raha hai ke gehun ki safed roti khaaun jo ghi aur doodh mein goondhi gaee ho.'' to logon mein se eik shakhs utha aur pakwa kar ley aaya aur aap ki khidmat mein pesh kar di. aapney puchha : ''ye ghi kis chiz mein tha ?'' usney kaha ke saandey ki khaal ki kuppi mein , aapney farmaya : ''usey utha lo . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye hadees munkar hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : sanad mein mazkur Ayub , Ayub sakhtiyaan nahin hai."
3819,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke tabuk mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko paneer pesh kya gaya to aapney chhuri mangwai aur phir bismillah padh kar usey kaata.
3820,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sirka behtareen salan hai.''
3821,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : '' sirka behtareen salan hai.''"
3822,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne lehsun ya piyaz khai ho wo ham se alag rahey . . . ya farmaya ke hamari masjid se alag rahey . . . usey chahiye ke apney ghar mein betha rahey .'' ( eik baar (aap ke samney Tabaaq pesh kya gaya , us mein kaee tarah ki sabziyan thin . aapney us mein bu mehsoos ki aur daryaft farmaya to jo sabziyan us mein thin sab batai gaeen . aapney farmaya : ''usey us shakhs ke qarib kar do .'' (yani us sahabi ke jo aap ke paas tha. ( jab usney aap ko dekha (ke aapney nahin khaya ( to usney bhi usey khana pasand na kya. aapney farmaya : ''tum khao , kyonkey mein) bahut qarib sey) us se baat karta hun jis se tum nahin kartey. Ahmed bin Saleh ne lafz ( Badr ( ki wazahat kartey huey farmaya ke ibne-Wahab ne uska tarjama '' tabaq '' ( Tabaaq ( kya hai."
3823,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas lehsun aur piyaz ka zikr kya gaya , aur kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! un tamam mein se lehsun ( ki bu) ziyada sakht hai to kya aap usey haram qarar detey hain? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum usey khao aur tum mein se jo usey khaye to wo us masjid ke qarib na aaye yahan tak ke us se uski badbu khatam ho jaey.''"
3824,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, raawi ka khayal hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, farmaya : '' jisney qibley ki taraf thooka to qiyamat ke din wo shakhs us haal mein aaeyga ke uska thook uski aakhon ke darmiyan laga hoga , aur jisney ye naa-pasandida sabzi khai ho wo hergiz hamari masjid ke qarib na aaye '' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye baat teen baar farmaai."
3825,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney ye sabzii khai ho ( lehsun aur piyaz ( to wo hergiz masjidon ke qarib na jaey.''
3826,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine eik din lehsun khaya phir masjide-nabawi mein hazir hua . meri eik rakat faut ho gaee thi. jab main masjid mein dakhil hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lehsun ki bo mehsus farmaai. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz mukammal ki to farmaya : ''jo shakhs ye sabzi khaye wo hergiz hamarey qarib na aaye yahan tak ke uski bu zaayel ho jaey.'' phir jab maine apni Namaz puri ki to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki qasam ! aap mujhey apna haath zarur pakdaayeingey. chunanche maine aap ka daste-mubarak lekar apni qamis ki aasteen mein se ley ja kar apney seeney par rakha to us waqt mera seena bandha hua tha. aapney farmaya : '' beshak tum mazoor ho.''
3827,Hazrat Muawiya bin Qurra apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne in do sabziyon se mana kya hai aur farmaya hai : '' jisney ye khai hun wo hergiz hamari masjid ke qarib na aaye .'' aur farmaya : ''agar tum ne unhen zarur hi khana ho to paka kar unki bu khatam kar liya karo.'' raawi ne kaha ke un sabziyon se murad piyaz aur lehsun hai.
3828,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke lehsun khaney se mana kya gaya hai siwaye uskey ke paka hua ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke sanad mein mazkur raawi '' shareek '' se murad shareek bin Hanbal hai.
3829,Abu Ziyad khiyaar bin Salma ne ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se piyaz ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : aakhiri khana jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaya us mein piyaz shamil thi.
3830,Hazrat Yusuf bin Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney jo ki roti ka tukda liya aur us par khajoor rakhi aur farmaya : ''ye uska salan hai.''
3831,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jis ghar mein khajoor na ho wo ghar waley bhookey hain.''
3832,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney purani khajoor pesh ki gaee to aap usey khol khol kar achi tarah jayeza letey aur sursuriyaan nikal detey they.
3833,Is-haq bin Abdullah bin Ubai Talha se marwi (bayan) hai ke) kabhi-kabhi ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aisi khajoor bhi pesh kar di jati thi jis mein kida laga hota tha. aur phir mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya.
3834,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do do ya teen teen khajuren ikhatti utha kar khaney se mana farmaya hai siwaey iske ke tum apney sathiyon se ijazat ley lo .
3835,Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kakdi aur taza khajoor mila kar khaya kartey they.
3836,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tarbuz aur taza khajoor mila kar khaya kartey they aur farmatey : '' ham is ( khajur ( ki garmi ka is (tarbuz) ki thandak se aur uski thandak ka uski garmi se tod kartey hain.''
3837,Sulaim bin Aamir ne Basar ke do beton se riwayat kya jo qabeela bano Sulaim se they (aur unka naam Abdullah aur Atiya naqal huey hain ( unhoney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye to ham ne aap ki khidmat mein makkhan aur khajoor pesh ki aur aap makkhan aur khajoor pasand farmaya kartey they.
3838,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein jihad par jatey they to ham mushrikon se bartan aur mishkeezey lekar istimal kar letey they aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey aeb na samajhtey they.
3839,"Hazrat Abu Solba khushni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya ke ham ehle-kitab ki ham-saayegi mein rehtey hain jabke wo apni haandiyon mein khinzir pakaatey aur apney bartanon mein sharab peetey hain, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumhen koi aur bartan mil jaeyn to un mein khao aur piyo aur agar unke ilawa koi aur na milen to unhen pani se achi tarah dho kar un mein kha pi liya karo.''"
3840,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen ( eik muhim mein) rawana farmaya aur Hazrat abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ko hamara ameer muqarrar farmaya , ham ne Quraish ka eik qafla pakadna tha. aapney hamen zaade-raah ke taur par eik thelaa khajuron ka inayat farmaya , hamen uskey ilawa aur kuch na mila to Hazrat abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) hamen eik eik dana khajoor diya kartey they ham usey choostey rehtey jaisey ke bacha choostaa hai, phir us par pani pi letey to wo hamen eik din raat tak ke liye kifaayat karta tha. aur ham apni lathiyon se darakhton se pattey jhaadtey , unhen pani mein bhigo letey , phir unhen kha jatey they. unhoney bayan kya ke ham sahil samandar ke sath sath chaley to hamen eik bahut badey tiley jaisi chiz nazar aai . ham uskey paas pahunchey to wo eik jandaar chiz thi jisey anbar kaha jata hai. Hazrat abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye murdar hai jo hamarey liye halal nahin, phir kehney lagey nahin, balke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bhejey huey hain aur Allah ki raah mein nikley hain aur uskey mohtaj bhi hain lihaza tum usey kha saktey ho. chunanche ham wahan uskey paas eik mahina tak rahey, hamari tadaad teen so thi ( ham us mein se khatey rahey ( yahan tak ke ham farba ho gaey . phir jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to ham ne aap se uska zikr kya. aapney farmaya : '' wo rizq tha jo Allah taala ne tumharey liye nikala tha, kya us mein se kuch tumharey paas hai to hamen bhi khilao ?'' chunanche ham ne us mein se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja jisey aapney khaya ."
3841,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke ghi mein chuha gir gaya , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya gaya to aapney farmaya : '' ( choohaa aur) uskey sath sath jo hai wo gira do aur baqi kha lo .''"
3842,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ghi mein chuha gir jaey to agar wo jama hua ho to chuha aur uskey ird-gird jo ho usey gira do aur agar wo sayyaal ( pighla hua (ho to uskey qarib mat jao . Hasan (bin Ali ( ne kaha ke abdur-Razzaaq ne bayan kya ke Maamer ne ye riwayat kaee dafa Zohri ki sanad sey, Ubaidullah bin Abdullah sey, unhoney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, unhoney ummul-momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan ki ."
3843,"Ahmed bin Saleh ne bayan kya ke hamen abdur-Razzaaq ne khabar di , unhoney kaha hamen Abdur-Rehman bin Bu-Zoya ne Maamer se khabar di , unhoney Zohri sey, unhoney Ubaidullah bin Abdullah sey, unhoney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, unhoney ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se. usi ( hadees (ke misl riwayat ki jo Zohri ne ibn Musaiyab se riwayat ki hai."
3844,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumharey kisi ke bartan mein makkhi gir jaey to usey usi mein dubo lo , bila-shuba uskey eik par mein bimari aur doosrey mein shifa hoti hai, aur ye apney bimari waley par se apna bachao karti hai, lihaza usey sari ko dubo lena chahiye .''"
3845,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab khana tanaawul farma letey to apni teeno ungliyon ko chaat letey aur farmatey : ''jab kisi ka luqma gir jaey to chahiye ke us se lagi gandagi ko door karkey usey kha ley aur usey shetan ke liye na chhodey .'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen hukm diya ke ham plate ko ungli se saaf kar liya keren aur farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi ko maloom nahin ke tuaam ke kis hissey mein uskey liye barkat dali gaee hai.''
3846,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumhara khaadim tumharey liye khana tayyar karkey tumhen pesh karey, jabkey wo uski garmi aur dhuwan bardasht karta raha ho to chahiye ke usey apney sath bitha kar khilaaey , agar khana kam aur uskey talabgar ziyada hon to ( bhi) munasib hai ke eik do luqmey uskey haath par rakh dey .''"
3847,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khana khaye to us waqt tak apna haath rumaal se na poonchhey jab tak ke usey chaat na ley ya chatwaa na ley.''"
3848,Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khana teen ungliyon se khaya kartey they aur apna haath us waqt tak nahin poonchhtey they jab tak ke usko chaat nahin letey they.
3849,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dasterkhaan utha liye janey ke baad ye dua padha kartey they (الحمد لله كثيرا طيبا مباركا فيه غير مكفي ولا مودع ولا مستغنى عنه ربنا) '' her qism ki tareef Allah hi ke liye hai bahut ziyada pakizah aur barkat dali gaee hai us mein , na kifaayat kya gaya (ke mazeed ki zarurat na rahey (aur na usey wadaa' ( chhoda ( kya gaya hai aur na us se be-niaz hua ja sakta hai aey hamarey rab .''"
3850,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab khaney se farigh hotey to ye padha kartey they ( الحمد لله الذي أطعمنا وسقانا وجعلنا مسلمين ( '' sab tareefen us Allah hi ke liye hain jisney hamen khilaya , pilaya aur musalman banaya .''"
3851,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kuch khatey pitey to yun kaha kartey they ( الحمد لله الذي أطعم وسقى , وسوغه , وجعل له مخرجا ( '' hamd us Allah ki jisney khilaya , pilaya , usey khushgawar banaya aur uskey bahir nikalney ka nizam bhi bana diya .''"
3852,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs is haal mein so gaya ke uskey haath par chiknaai lagi reh gaee aur usney usko dhoya nahin aur phir usey kuch ho gaya to apney aap hi ko malamat karey.''"
3853,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke abul-Haisam bin Tehan (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye khaney ka ehtimam kya aur aap ko aap ke Sahaba ko bulaya . chunanche jab wo farigh ho gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney bhai ko uska iwaz pesh karo.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! uska iwaz aur badal kya ho? aapney farmaya : ''jab kisi ke ghar jaya jaey, uska khana khaya jaey, pani piya jaey to uskey liye dua ki jaey. yehi uska iwaz aur badal hai.''"
3854,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Janab Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif ley gaey to unhoney roti aur raughan zaitun pesh kya, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey khaya , phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yun farmaya ( أفطر عندكم الصائمون وأكل طعامكم الأبرار وصلت عليكم الملائكة ( '' rozey daar tumharey yahan iftaar kya karen, nek saleh log tumhara khana khaya karen aur farishtey tumhen duayen diya keren .''"
